Description: IBANEZ ORM-1 OMAR RODRIGUEZ LOPEZ SIGNATURE ELECTRIC GUITARJUST HAD A FULL SET-UP INC NEW STRINGS! The neck is nice and chunky! The action has been set med/low, the frets are in great shape and the neck is straight with no problems what so ever. The electronics work as they should with no crackling and the single pickup sounds amazing! This model is quite rare now so snap this up whilst you can! The pickup has been upgraded to a Seymour Duncan mini humbucker and a tone control has been added. This was all carried out by a professional. The original guitar didn't have a tone control. The guitar has just had a full setup including:New set of strings (d'addario11's)Fret polish Intonation adjustment Neck relief adjustment String action adjustmentAny questions drop me an email The images included in this listing are of the actual guitar for sale, (amp cab not included!).
